data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!!!   Welcome to this stunning fully upgraded home nestled in the heart of Union Park. The moment you arrive, you'll be captivated by the flourishing landscape and charming decorative curbing. A wide driveway leads you to the paved entryway, boasting modern amenities like an electronic keyless entry system.  Once inside, you'll be greeted by a neutral palette and an abundance of natural light, creating an inviting atmosphere. To the left of the entryway, you'll find a convenient desk area and a half bath.  The spacious open living area on the ground floor features large ceramic tile flooring. The kitchen is a dream, featuring expansive granite countertops, an abundance of cabinetry, and an extra wide island with multiple barstool seating options. The elegant espresso cabinetry is complemented by a stylish backsplash, satin nickel hardware, and crown molding, all upgraded to a height of 42 inches. Stainless steel appliances and a walk-in pantry lend to a chef's dream.  This beauty features a large open concept including the dining room, living room and kitchen all in one. Sliding doors lead to a covered lanai and a partially fenced yard. Heading upstairs, you'll be welcomed by a versatile loft area, ideal for a media/computer space, play area, with many other options for your convenience. The secondary bedrooms are generously sized, and the secondary bath features a double vanity and a separate combination tub/shower, making getting ready a breeze. The convenience continues with an upstairs utility room for laundry. The expansive Owners Suite awaits, with lots of natural light streaming in through energy-efficient windows. The large walk-in closet provides an abundance of storage, satisfying all your organizational needs. The en-suite bath boasts additional storage in a linen closet, as well as a separate garden tub, shower, and water closet. Union Park offers a wealth of amenities, including walking trails, exercise stops, a community pool, a clubhouse, splash pad, dog park and much more.  High-speed fiber internet and cable are INCLUDED! This gem not only offers you a home, but a chance to be part of a beautiful community.  Live the life that you deserve and schedule your tour today.
